{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UPBe2EPB2cFqig2QSNWuXq","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tid: \"PRD-549.1\"\n3\ttitle: \"Pytest config, wheel exclusion, and conftest split\"\n4\tkind: task\n5\tstatus: ready\n6\tpriority: medium\n7\teffort: s\n8\tcapability: simple\n9\tparent: \"[[PRD-549-builtins-package-split]]\"\n10\tdepends_on: []\n11\tblocks:\n12\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3a-move-ensure-worktree]]\"\n13\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3b-move-set-status]]\"\n14\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3c-move-commit]]\"\n15\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3d-move-push-branch]]\"\n16\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3e-move-summarize-agent-run]]\"\n17\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3f-move-commit-transcript]]\"\n18\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3g-move-create-pr]]\"\n19\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3h-move-lint-attribution]]\"\n20\t  - \"[[PRD-549.3i-move-cleanup-worktree]]\"\n21\timpacts:\n22\t  - pyproject.toml\n23\t  - conftest.py\n24\t  - tests/conftest.py\n25\tworkflow: null\n26\ttarget_version: null\n27\tcreated: 2026-04-08\n28\tupdated: 2026-04-08\n29\ttags:\n30\t  - refactor\n31\t  - tests\n32\t  - organization\n33\t---\n34\t\n35\t# Pytest config, wheel exclusion, and conftest split\n36\t\n37\t## Summary\n38\t\n39\tConfigure pytest to discover colocated `*_test.py` files alongside standard `test_*.py` files, exclude test files from the built wheel, and split `conftest.py` so shared fixtures are available to both `tests/` and colocated unit tests.\n40\t\n41\tThis is the foundational infrastructure task — all per-builtin migration tasks depend on the test discovery and conftest changes landing first.\n42\t\n43\t## Requirements\n44\t\n45\t1. Update `[tool.pytest.ini_options]` in `pyproject.toml`:\n46\t   - `testpaths = [\"src\", \"tests\", \"workflows\"]`\n47\t   - `python_files = [\"test_*.py\", \"*_test.py\"]`\n48\t   - `addopts = \"--import-mode=importlib\"`\n49\t2. Update the build backend config to exclude `**/*_test.py` and `**/conftest.py` from the built wheel.\n50\t3. Split `tests/conftest.py`: move truly project-wide fixtures to a repo-root `conftest.py`, keep integration-specific fixtures in `tests/conftest.py`.\n51\t4. Add a throwaway colocated test file (e.g. `src/darkfactory/prd_test.py` with a trivial assertion) to verify discovery works. Remove or replace before merge.\n52\t5. Build the wheel and verify no `*_test.py` files are inside it.\n53\t\n54\t## Technical Approach\n55\t\n56\t### `pyproject.toml` changes\n57\t\n58\t```toml\n59\t[tool.pytest.ini_options]\n60\ttestpaths = [\"src\", \"tests\", \"workflows\"]\n61\tpython_files = [\"test_*.py\", \"*_test.py\"]\n62\taddopts = \"--import-mode=importlib\"\n63\t```\n64\t\n65\t### Wheel exclusion\n66\t\n67\tCheck the build backend in `pyproject.toml`. If Hatchling:\n68\t\n69\t```toml\n70\t[tool.hatch.build.targets.wheel]\n71\texclude = [\"**/*_test.py\", \"**/conftest.py\"]\n72\t```\n73\t\n74\tIf setuptools, use the equivalent `exclude` pattern.\n75\t\n76\t### conftest.py split\n77\t\n78\t- Read `tests/conftest.py` and identify which fixtures are used by tests across both `tests/` and `src/`.\n79\t- Move shared fixtures to a new repo-root `conftest.py`.\n80\t- Keep integration-only fixtures in `tests/conftest.py`.\n81\t\n82\t### Verification\n83\t\n84\t```bash\n85\tuv build\n86\t# Unzip the wheel and assert no *_test.py files\n87\tpython -c \"import zipfile; z=zipfile.ZipFile('dist/*.whl'); assert not [f for f in z.namelist() if f.endswith('_test.py')]\"\n88\t```\n89\t\n90\t## Acceptance Criteria\n91\t\n92\t- [ ] AC-1: `pyproject.toml` configures pytest to discover both `test_*.py` and `*_test.py` across `src/`, `tests/`, and `workflows/` with `--import-mode=importlib`.\n93\t- [ ] AC-2: All existing tests pass under the new config (`just test` green).\n94\t- [ ] AC-3: A colocated `*_test.py` file under `src/darkfactory/` is discovered and run by pytest.\n95\t- [ ] AC-4: A built wheel contains zero `*_test.py` files.\n96\t- [ ] AC-5: Repo-root `conftest.py` provides shared fixtures to both `tests/` and colocated unit tests.\n97\t- [ ] AC-6: `just lint`, `just typecheck`, and `just format-check` all pass.\n98\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fdfb98d4-32e9-4fa7-a46c-bf4d30fd4fa2","uuid":"6c65e822-c4d1-4e06-ae6b-bb7503ddd4b3","timestamp":"2026-04-09T02:18:00.682Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/sksizer2/Developer/DarkFactory/.worktrees/PRD-549-builtins-package-split/prds/PRD-549.1-pytest-config-wheel-conftest.md","content":"---\nid: \"PRD-549.1\"\ntitle: \"Pytest config, wheel exclusion, and conftest split\"\nkind: task\nstatus: ready\npriority: medium\neffort: s\ncapability: simple\nparent: \"[[PRD-549-builtins-package-split]]\"\ndepends_on: []\nblocks:\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3a-move-ensure-worktree]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3b-move-set-status]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3c-move-commit]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3d-move-push-branch]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3e-move-summarize-agent-run]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3f-move-commit-transcript]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3g-move-create-pr]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3h-move-lint-attribution]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-549.3i-move-cleanup-worktree]]\"\nimpacts:\n  - pyproject.toml\n  - conftest.py\n  - tests/conftest.py\nworkflow: null\ntarget_version: null\ncreated: 2026-04-08\nupdated: 2026-04-08\ntags:\n  - refactor\n  - tests\n  - organization\n---\n\n# Pytest config, wheel exclusion, and conftest split\n\n## Summary\n\nConfigure pytest to discover colocated `*_test.py` files alongside standard `test_*.py` files, exclude test files from the built wheel, and split `conftest.py` so shared fixtures are available to both `tests/` and colocated unit tests.\n\nThis is the foundational infrastructure task — all per-builtin migration tasks depend on the test discovery and conftest changes landing first.\n\n## Requirements\n\n1. Update `[tool.pytest.ini_options]` in `pyproject.toml`:\n   - `testpaths = [\"src\", \"tests\", \"workflows\"]`\n   - `python_files = [\"test_*.py\", \"*_test.py\"]`\n   - `addopts = \"--import-mode=importlib\"`\n2. Update the build backend config to exclude `**/*_test.py` and `**/conftest.py` from the built wheel.\n3. Split `tests/conftest.py`: move truly project-wide fixtures to a repo-root `conftest.py`, keep integration-specific fixtures in `tests/conftest.py`.\n4. Add a throwaway colocated test file (e.g. `src/darkfactory/prd_test.py` with a trivial assertion) to verify discovery works. Remove or replace before merge.\n5. Build the wheel and verify no `*_test.py` files are inside it.\n\n## Technical Approach\n\n### `pyproject.toml` changes\n\n```toml\n[tool.pytest.ini_options]\ntestpaths = [\"src\", \"tests\", \"workflows\"]\npython_files = [\"test_*.py\", \"*_test.py\"]\naddopts = \"--import-mode=importlib\"\n```\n\n### Wheel exclusion\n\nCheck the build backend in `pyproject.toml`. If Hatchling:\n\n```toml\n[tool.hatch.build.targets.wheel]\nexclude = [\"**/*_test.py\", \"**/conftest.py\"]\n```\n\nIf setuptools, use the equivalent `exclude` pattern.\n\n### conftest.py split\n\n- Read `tests/conftest.py` and identify which fixtures are used by tests across both `tests/` and `src/`.\n- Move shared fixtures to a new repo-root `conftest.py`.\n- Keep integration-only fixtures in `tests/conftest.py`.\n\n### Verification\n\n```bash\nuv build\n# Unzip the wheel and assert no *_test.py files\npython -c \"import zipfile; z=zipfile.ZipFile('dist/*.whl'); assert not [f for f in z.namelist() if f.endswith('_test.py')]\"\n```\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC-1: `pyproject.toml` configures pytest to discover both `test_*.py` and `*_test.py` across `src/`, `tests/`, and `workflows/` with `--import-mode=importlib`.\n- [ ] AC-2: All existing tests pass under the new config (`just test` green).\n- [ ] AC-3: A colocated `*_test.py` file under `src/darkfactory/` is discovered and run by pytest.\n- [ ] AC-4: A built wheel contains zero `*_test.py` files.\n- [ ] AC-5: Repo-root `conftest.py` provides shared fixtures to both `tests/` and colocated unit tests.\n- [ ] AC-6: `just lint`, `just typecheck`, and `just format-check` all pass.\n","numLines":98,"startLine":1,"totalLines":98}}}
